				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I am an Iksar Necro that recently did this quest. I got my book from a NPC named Crusader Zixo in East Cabilis down near the Warriors guild. I took it to the Toilmaster and got the Hammer of Exoneration and the sac. After getting the mortar and pestel from the mortician I went out and got enough bone fragments crushed up into powder to fill seven of the eight slots in the sac. After combining with one bottle of bloodwater (which I bought from a vendor in E. Cab) I fashioned a new item, a bag(can't remember exactly what it was called). I then took my new bag and my book back to Crusader Zixo, gave it too him and he gave me a giant weapon, spear of some sort, something &quot;Pike&quot;. 46 delay 8 dam weight 13 ac 1. The point is it is NO DROP LORE ITEM for Iksar Warriors only. I was thoroughly disappointed being a Necro, having collected all those bone fragments with that 60 delay Hammer. I tried to sell it only to be offered about 2gold 9silv for it. I hope this post helps any Iks Wars out there. I will post later with the exact name of the weapon.<BR>
